# Riddim Toolkit

A MIDI groove‚Äêgeneration toolkit focused on reggae, rocksteady, and ska.  

## Installation

```bash
git clone https://github.com/you/riddim-toolkit.git
cd riddim-toolkit
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

## Usage

```bash
python performance_builder_gui.py
```
1. Select a MIDI output port.  
2. Choose bank & patch for each part.  
3. Click **Send to JV-1080**.  

## Running Tests

```bash
pip install pytest
pytest
```

## Groove Generator

See `scripts/riddim_generator.py` for API usage and examples.